---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Writings
description: Essays and short-form writing by Richard Caballero.
---
<section>
  <h1>Writings</h1>
  <p class="lead">
    Essays, notes, and reflections on GIS, AI, design leadership, and technology.
  </p>
</section>

<section>
  <ul class="list">
    {% for post in collections.writings | reverse %}
      <li>
        <article>
          <h3><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h3>
          <p class="meta">{{ post.data.date | formatDate }} · {{ post.data.form }}</p>
          {% if post.data.summary %}
            <p>{{ post.data.summary }}</p>
          {% endif %}
        </article>
      </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
</section>
